      <p>** Items **</p>
      <p>- Warrior and Magician epic changes &#8211; A new version of these two
        epic items is available to accommodate the new item augmentations. Both
        of these epics are basically summoned items, and therefore they would
        lose any augmentations when used or unsummoned. Players wishing to change
        these items into &quot;permanent&quot; versions in order to augment them
